### 환경 설정
@base = http://localhost:3000
@accessToken =

### 내 프로필 업데이트 (비밀번호 포함)
PATCH {{base}}/api/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "기존비밀번호",
  "newPassword": "새비밀번호1234!"
}

### 비밀번호 변경
PATCH {{base}}/api/users/password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "기존비밀번호",
  "newPassword": "새비밀번호1234!"
}
